comment: Hill (IND) Lowry (TOR) connect at around mid-court. Hill maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Lowry.
Ellis (IND) and Valanciunas (TOR) engage and separate away from the ball.
Carroll (TOR) and George (IND) make incidental contact while chasing the loose ball.
Hill (IND) makes contact with Lowry's (TOR) face as he reaches in for the steal.
DeRozan (TOR) makes incidental contact with George (IND) that does not affect his ability to defend.
Lowry (TOR) and George (IND) make incidental contact with one another.
[Observable in enhanced video] DeRozan (TOR) hops on the same foot during his spin move.
Hill (IND) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Carroll's (TOR) drive and shot attempt.
Mahinmi (IND) and Valanciunas (TOR) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
DeRozan (TOR) does not obtain a legal guarding position and makes body contact with George (IND) that affects his RSBQ.
Joseph (TOR) firms up as he sets the screen on Hill (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Valanciunas (TOR) and Mahinmi (IND) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
RATR shows that Carroll (TOR) makes incidental contact with Hill (IND) as they position for the rebound, and makes contact with the ball following the missed field goal attempt.
Carroll (TOR) and George (IND) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
DeRozan (TOR) makes body contact with Mahinmi (IND), dislodging him and affecting his ability to catch the alley-oop pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] LATR shows that DeRozan (TOR) hops on the same foot during his spin move.
Hill (IND) commits a take foul on DeRozan (TOR).
Turner (IND) sets a screen on Carroll (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Carroll (TOR) legally contests George (IND) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Turner (IND) commits a take foul on Biyombo (TOR).
